SQL_STMT_U.val: select ICPH.ICPH_BANKID, ICPH.ICPH_BANKACCOUNT, ICPH.ICPH_BANK_CURRENCY, min(ICPH_BANK_ADMNO), min(ICPH_BANK_LEDG_NO) from :1/ICPH ICPH where ICPH.ICPH_ADMNO = :2 and ICPH.ICPH_CLNTNO = :3 and ICPH.ICPH_ROWTYPE = 1 and ICPH.ICPH_DATDAILYSTATEMENT > ':4' and exists(select * from :1/BNKA where BNKA_BANKACCOUNT like '%'||trim(ICPH.ICPH_BANKACCOUNT)||'%' and BNKA_BANKID=ICPH.ICPH_BANKID and ((BNKA_ADMNO1 = :2 and BNKA_CLNTNO1 = :3) or (BNKA_ADMNO2 = :2 and BNKA_CLNTNO2 = :3) or (BNKA_ADMNO3 = :2 and BNKA_CLNTNO3 = :3) or (BNKA_ADMNO4 = :2 and BNKA_CLNTNO4 = :3) or (BNKA_ADMNO5 = :2 and BNKA_CLNTNO5 = :3))) group by ICPH.ICPH_BANKID, ICPH.ICPH_BANKACCOUNT, ICPH.ICPH_BANK_CURRENCY order by ICPH.ICPH_BANKID, ICPH.ICPH_BANKACCOUNT, ICPH.ICPH_BANK_CURRENCY for fetch only

SQL_STMT_U.val: select max(TIBT_DATDAILYSTATEMENT) from :1/TIBT where TIBT_ADMNO = :2 and TIBT_CLNTNO = :3 and TIBT_BANKID = :4 and TIBT_BANKACCOUNT =':5' and (TIBT_NPAYMENTSHANDLED*100/case when TIBT_NPAYMENTS = 0 then 1 else TIBT_NPAYMENTS end) >= :6 for fetch only

select cast(sum(TIBT_NPAYMENTS) as decimal (9,0)), cast(sum(TIBT_NPAYMENTSHANDLED) as decimal (9,0)) from :1/TIBT where TIBT_ADMNO = :2 and TIBT_CLNTNO = :3 and TIBT_BANKID = :4 and TIBT_BANKACCOUNT = ':5' and TIBT_DATDAILYSTATEMENT = ':6' for fetch only

select cast(sum(ICPH_TOTAMOUNTC) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/ICPH where ICPH_ADMNO = :2 and ICPH_CLNTNO = :3 and ICPH_BANKID = :4 and ICPH_BANKACCOUNT = ':5' and ICPH_ROWTYPE = 1 and ICPH_DATDAILYSTATEMENT > ':6' for fetch only
select min(CLAP_HANDLEDUNTILDATE) from :1/CLAP where CLAP_CLAC_NO = :2 and CLAP_HANDLEDUNTILDATE is not null for fetch only

select cast(sum(SCHI_INVAMOUNTC) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/SCHI where SCHI_SCHT_NO = :2 and (SCHI_MARKCODETEXT = :3 or SCHI_MARKCODE = :3 or SCHI_MARKCODETEXT = :4 or SCHI_MARKCODE = :4) for fetch only
select cast(sum(SCHI_INVAMOUNTC) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/SCHI where SCHI_SCHT_NO = :2 and :3 and SCHI_INVDELETED = 'N' for fetch only
select cast(sum(INVO_AACTUALC) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/INVO where INVO_ADMNO = :2 and INVO_CLNTNO = :3 and INVO_AACTUALC <> 0 and :4 and INVO_DEBH_NO = 1 for fetch only
select cast(sum(CLAP_REQUIRED_OMQ059) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/CLAP where CLAP_CLAC_NO = :2 for fetch only
select cast(sum(CLAP_DIRECTPAYMENTS) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/CLAP where CLAP_CLAC_NO = :2 for fetch only
